erts zorgen ervoor dat jouw medewerkers methodisch leren werken met Microsoft 365 programma’s. Deze methode, de adoptiestraat, is al bij vele ShareValue-klanten met groot succes uitgevoerd. Wordt jouw organisatie de volgende?","Meer weten over de ShareValue adoptiestraat?","White",{"id":232,"name":233,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":19,"height":191,"formats":234,"hash":255,"ext":23,"mime":26,"size":256,"url":257,"previewUrl":18,"provider":58,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":258,"updatedAt":258,"documentId":259,"publishedAt":61,"focalPoint":18},783,"adoptie.jpg",{"large":235,"small":240,"medium":245,"thumbnail":250},{"ext":23,"url":236,"hash":237,"mime":26,"name":238,"path":18,"size":239,"width":29,"height":198},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa.jpg","large_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa","large_adoptie.jpg",140.54,{"ext":23,"url":241,"hash":242,"mime":26,"name":243,"path":18,"size":244,"width":20,"height":204},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa.jpg","small_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa","small_adoptie.jpg",46.09,{"ext":23,"url":246,"hash":247,"mime":26,"name":248,"path":18,"size":249,"width":44,"height":210},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/medium_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa.jpg","medium_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa","medium_adoptie.jpg",90.06,{"ext":23,"url":251,"hash":252,"mime":26,"name":253,"path":18,"size":254,"width":216,"height":217},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/thumbnail_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa.jpg","thumbnail_adoptie_dc3bbcacaa","thumbnail_adoptie.jpg",13.08,"adoptie_dc3bbcacaa",204.86,"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/adoptie_dc3bbcacaa.jpg","2024-08-08T09:47:03.256Z","kqdvjnnutm27pjz49n0b8l8r",{"id":261,"title":262,"subTitle":263,"content":264,"callToActionText":18,"callToActionLink":18,"colorStyle":186,"showAsides":187,"imageUrl":265,"__component":223},31,"Microsoft trends","Advies over de nieuwste Microsoft-ontwikkelingen","M